{
  "name": "Horde Encounter: 3-PC Party vs 5 Goblins + Hobgoblin Captain (multi-round AoE + concentration + resource depletion)",
  "description": "Multi-PC party (Fighter, Cleric, Wizard) at L5 faces 6 enemies — 5 Goblins clustered for AoE spells + 1 Hobgoblin Captain. 8+ rounds. Tests: (1) Fireball AoE hits multiple clustered targets, (2) Bless concentration across 3 allies resilient to multi-turn, (3) Extra Attack into hordes, (4) Spell slot depletion over the encounter, (5) Cleric healing triage via Cure Wounds + Healing Word, (6) initiative ordering with 9 combatants. Uses defaultBehavior endTurn to keep PC damage deterministic (the true test is PC resource mgmt + AoE coverage).",
